          <a href="/donate" class="inline-block px-6 md:px-8 py-3 md:py-4 bg-tertiary text-white rounded-xl font-bold transition-transform hover:-translate-y-1 active:scale-95 shadow-lg shadow-tertiary/25 text-sm md:text-base">
            Start Donating Today
